      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Available is a 2008 BMW M3 (E92) featuring the high-revving S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8. This unit delivers linear power up to its 8,400 RPM redline through a precise 6-speed manual gearbox. The chassis remains taut with a functional M Variable Differential Lock providing excellent lateral traction. Recent preventative maintenance includes rod bearing replacement and throttle body actuator service, ensuring the individual throttle bodies (ITBs) and double-VANOS system operate within factory specifications. The suspension geometry is stock, retaining the original damping characteristics. While the exterior shows minor road-derived patina consistent with a well-loved driver's car, the mechanical integrity remains robust for the next enthusiast.",
